definitions.text:
@làm ma
- Hold burial rites for
=Làm ma chu tất cho bố+To hold decent burial rites for one's dead father, to give one's father a decent funeral

@làm màu
- Grow subsidiary crops
=Làm màu sau khi gặt vụ lúa chính+To grow subsidiary crops after harvesting the main rice crop

@làm mẫu
* verb
- to serve as a model
